.worktrees/

# Local project instructions
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
.github/copilot-instructions.md

# Ansible-rendered prod config (compose_project role on the prod host).
# Not tracked — rendered fresh from vault each apply.
/mediawiki/
/secrets/

# ML model data (weights + tag-vocab CSVs) is provisioned on hosts from
# HuggingFace, not committed — the vocab CSV also carries the full danbooru tag
# list (incl. explicit tag names we never map). Track only the READMEs that
# document how to fetch each model.
ml_models/**
!ml_models/**/
!ml_models/**/README.md
